    "description": "即使他们被击败，邪神也从未真正死亡。他们耐心地沉眠，等待时机，直到再次崛起的机会来临。<br><br>《Morbid:The Lords of Ire》是继广受好评的等距魂系 ARPG 《Morbid:The Seven Acolytes》后的下一力作，英勇的 Striver 者再次回归，在黑暗扭曲的痛苦世界中与可怕的生物展开斗争.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/a4bcb2cfef85edbaf619d601fa6d553f.poster.avif?t=1716972671\" width=572 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/a4bcb2cfef85edbaf619d601fa6d553f.webm?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/a4bcb2cfef85edbaf619d601fa6d553f.mp4?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/979db8776bc7cf24c4fe301aef6926df.avif?t=1716972671\" width=612 height=102 /></span><br><br>以全新的 3D 视角对抗可怕的敌人。使用一系列致命武器、装备和祝福来屠杀可怕的生物，消灭你挡道的一切敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/7254003f1928ffdb46ad9bf6f6a7023d.avif?t=1716972671\" width=600 height=350 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/9977635da71f9ef004c63e4883d3269b.avif?t=1716972671\" width=612 height=102 /></span><br><br>建立在《Morbid:The Seven Acolytes》的理智系统基础上，你的战斗方式会对你周围的世界产生巨大的影响。屈服于癫狂可以带来巨大的力量，但风险也很大，并且会动态地改变你对周围世界的看法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/7b818e64ed2778d2ccab78eeec1df478.poster.avif?t=1716972671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/7b818e64ed2778d2ccab78eeec1df478.webm?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/7b818e64ed2778d2ccab78eeec1df478.mp4?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/c73ac6e02f98689eabc26d55f9b08c37.avif?t=1716972671\" width=612 height=102 /></span><br><br>在 Ire 的五个世界中奋战——从寒冷的山脉到腐烂的城市，在恐怖朋克之域，生存着五个独特的派系。履行你的神圣职责，驱逐降临在这片土地上的邪恶。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/738eb17a14a77548785f65e5e9e91683.poster.avif?t=1716972671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/738eb17a14a77548785f65e5e9e91683.webm?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/738eb17a14a77548785f65e5e9e91683.mp4?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/e90c7e4359893c44a53a8151c34419b6.avif?t=1716972671\" width=612 height=102 /></span><br><br>追捕可怕的敌人，并挑战艾尔之王。更多鲜血，更多胆识量，更多 Morbid。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/150925f489d998df29bfc54138c6e339.poster.avif?t=1716972671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/150925f489d998df29bfc54138c6e339.webm?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/150925f489d998df29bfc54138c6e339.mp4?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/f83743586626e902eff0dc9fc124e6ae.avif?t=1716972671\" width=612 height=102 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索五片独特土地上的多样化环境，及其噩梦般的景象和可怕的生物。<br></li><li>运用各种武器、符文和祝福来尝试不同的玩法<br></li><li>踏入疯狂的深渊，或走在理智的光辉下，定义你的风险和回报。<br></li><li>对抗五位可怕的艾尔之王，并追捕更多强敌<br></li><li>以全新 3D 视角充分领略《Morbid》的恐怖氛围。</li></ul>",
